{"type": "article", "id": 27302, "title": "匡威推出针织系列，以及，小众香水救了整个香水市场？｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-25T10:20:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 13655, "name": "Manolo Blahnik"}, {"id": 2483, "name": "康泰纳什"}, {"id": 28126, "name": "Advance Publications Inc"}, {"id": 28127, "name": "Marcolin"}, {"id": 16698, "name": "Dsquared2"}, {"id": 15559, "name": "L'Oreal"}, {"id": 5418, "name": "Bulgari"}, {"id": 28128, "name": "Buccellati"}, {"id": 15344, "name": "Mango"}, {"id": 1029, "name": "Lego"}, {"id": 28129, "name": "APOC"}, {"id": 18474, "name": "Free people"}, {"id": 2835, "name": "匡威"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 100, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133838bevhYCagZlFPndr0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/footwear/manolo-blahnik-expands-asia-japan-malaysia-singapore-10436240/\">Manolo Blahnik 要在亚洲扩张</a>｜亚洲奢侈品牌代理商 Bluebell 将帮助 Manolo Blahnik 在亚洲的扩张业务，主要瞄准日本、马来西亚和新加坡市场。计划秋季在日本做店中店，2017 年在东京开旗舰店，秋季计划在马来西亚开旗舰店。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/05/conde-nast-rent-the-runway\">康泰纳什集团要和服装租赁网站 Rent the Runway 合作，为员工提供每月服装租赁费</a> ｜为了让员工衣着光鲜地去上班，康泰纳什集团每月要为每位员工提供 139 美元的服装租赁费。此前，康泰纳什的母公司 Advance Publications Inc 用 6000 万美元投资了 Rent the Runway。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Marcolin-and-Dsquared2-extend-eyewear-partnership-to-2021,696193.html#.V0TkZWMjeT8\">Dsquared2 和意大利眼镜生产商 Marcolin 续约至 2021 年</a>｜ Marcolin 将继续设计、生产、分销 Dsquared2 的眼镜和太阳镜业务。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/L-Oreal-says-niche-perfumes-have-saved-the-market,695901.html#.V0TktGMjc9c\">L'Oréal 认为小众香水拯救了香水市场</a>｜ L'Oréal 估计小众香水市场价值 10 亿欧元，而且这个市场是香水市场中增长最快的品类，去年增加了 15%。然而价值 150 亿欧元的全球香水市场去年只增加了 2.9%。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Bulgari-aims-to-have-up-to-six-stores-in-Russia-over-10-years,696202.html#.V0TkdmMjeT8\">Bulgari 计划未来 10 年在俄罗斯增开 4 家店铺</a> ｜ 届时 Bulgari 在俄罗斯的店铺会有 6 家。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Richemont-in-talks-to-buy-Italian-jewellers-Buccellati,695931.html#.V0Tkq2MjeSM\">Richemont 计划收购意大利珠宝品牌Buccellati </a>｜ Buccellati 是创立于 1919 年的高级珠宝商，2015 年销售额为 4100 万欧元。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/jewelry/karlie-kloss-swarovski-10435845/\">Karlie Kloss 成了 Swarovski 新代言人。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133814x5sWd0vBZPYpMnm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213381465BpNzjZFAw9OH4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133815bghIQ8Jv57T3WX9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133815Bht3A4weJiNYuSlG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133816GoxpckFrXgYQvIq1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63183594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133816MFLgZspEKWYhaR34.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338173EBmFYNixLO0AKoy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">同 Marks &amp; Spencer, Uniqlo and Dolce &amp; Gabbana 一样，Mango 也瞄准了穆斯林市场，为斋月推出了一个特别的系列，包括夹克、土耳其式长衫、legging 等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133818CpXeJtL9hwPqnzvA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338187mDYnw9K68BslOed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133819OBbnjmxFL0KPMpW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133819I3EFf69yne0Ktxmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133820aoVmvSbkUBhp9Gfr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://shop.lego.com/en-NO/Big-Ben-21013\">LEGO Creator 系列推出英国大本钟的的积木</a>，由 4,163 块积木组成，组装后的钟楼约高 60 厘米。这个产品将于 6 月 1 日上架，定价为 250 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338203pJRYGQvZi1a2nqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133821AMO27iF18yS9nBus.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133821LSedHXuJNg2arETQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133822Gk3uwsIFlaZv08b2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/tags/a-piece-of-cake\">韩国品牌 A Piece of Cake（APOC）公布了 2016 春夏系列 Lookbook。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133822gjiHsp7XyDnFJoCT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133823UvSPaXHpCzL1nE96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133823Int6QjAd3b75GMfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133824mgNDZWLrH3G5psUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133825wETB2WJu4nj3zokH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133825fUPFAe8zNldgkrxu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133825akBUNHzegxJ9dmhE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133826O8yMVKq5Nr097zZm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133827YsLrl9jSmXKi6RV7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133827Fjas5H4riXRoA8Ik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133828XS8gfQxDL5aPIzqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338283m5USQcJYfuT0IMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.freshnessmag.com/2016/05/23/converse-chuck-taylor-ii-knit-collection-closer-look/\">Converse Chuck Taylor All Star II 推出全新的针织款系列，</a>有高帮和低帮两个样式，颜色有浅白、牛仔色，红色和黃色等。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133829ZCKmBN13wt2XUVv9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338298DfLxRbM7hC9zkol.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133830VbdQ2mlJeIjiZFBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133830hcpMTz2IEluL4qZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133832b0LIYHlAcnz47FP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338328qMzF5H04whuvjU7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338331Lyj6mZvbQdaTPOJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133833Jn27VUS9XamyhODw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/free-people-wedding-dresses-2016-shop/\">Free People 推出了 2016 年波西米亚风的婚纱。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133834t8FMUGVWfrp3gaj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133834MGD0RPpCU6TvtV2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213383563S1FpRJqb4CrGVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133835Q2wrpy0oZT3B1AJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133836I5kgJajnfBMm0eRo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133836LauYy0V8gZ7eP4BN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133837Jgz6YkuMAnBi5IQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"